{
  "type": "USJ",
  "version": "3.1",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "book",
      "marker": "id",
      "code": "OBA",
      "content": [
        "- Berean Study Bible"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "h",
      "content": [
        "Obadiah"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "toc1",
      "content": [
        "Obadiah"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "toc2",
      "content": [
        "Obadiah"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "toc3",
      "content": [
        "Obadiah"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "mt1",
      "content": [
        "Obadiah"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "chapter",
      "marker": "c",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "s1",
      "content": [
        "The Destruction of Edom"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "r",
      "content": [
        "(Jeremiah 49:7–22)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "p",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "1"
        },
        "This is the vision of Obadiah:"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "This is what the Lord GOD says about Edom—"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "b"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "We have heard a message from the LORD;"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "an envoy has been sent among the nations"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "to say, “Rise up,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "and let us go to battle against her!”—"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "b"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "2"
        },
        "“Behold, I will make you small among the nations;"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "you will be deeply despised."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "3"
        },
        "The pride of your heart has deceived you,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "O dwellers in the clefts of the rocks",
        {
          "type": "note",
          "marker": "f",
          "caller": "+",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "fr",
              "content": [
                "1:3 "
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "ft",
              "content": [
                "Or in the retreats of Sela"
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "whose habitation is the heights,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "who say in your heart,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "‘Who can bring me down to the ground?’"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "4"
        },
        "Though you soar like the eagle"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "and make your nest among the stars,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "even from there I will bring you down,”"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "qr",
      "content": [
        "declares the LORD."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "5"
        },
        "“If thieves came to you,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "if robbers by night—"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "oh, how you will be ruined—"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "would they not steal only what they wanted?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "If grape gatherers came to you,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "would they not leave some gleanings?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "6"
        },
        "But how Esau will be pillaged,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "his hidden treasures sought out!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "7"
        },
        "All the men allied with you"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "will drive you to the border;"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "the men at peace with you"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "will deceive and overpower you."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "Those who eat your bread",
        {
          "type": "note",
          "marker": "f",
          "caller": "+",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "fr",
              "content": [
                "1:7 "
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "ft",
              "content": [
                "Hebrew does not include Those who eat."
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "will set a trap for you"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "without your awareness of it."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "8"
        },
        "In that day, declares the LORD,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "will I not destroy the wise men of Edom"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "and the men of understanding"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "in the mountains of Esau?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "9"
        },
        "Then your mighty men, O Teman,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "will be terrified,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "so that everyone in the mountains of Esau"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "will be cut down in the slaughter."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "b"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "10"
        },
        "Because of the violence against your brother Jacob,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "you will be covered with shame"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "and cut off forever."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "11"
        },
        "On the day you stood aloof"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "while strangers carried off his wealth"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "and foreigners entered his gate"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "and cast lots for Jerusalem,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "you were just like one of them."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "12"
        },
        "But you should not gloat in that day,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "your brotherʼs day of misfortune,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "nor rejoice over the people of Judah"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "in the day of their destruction,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "nor boast proudly",
        {
          "type": "note",
          "marker": "f",
          "caller": "+",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "fr",
              "content": [
                "1:12 "
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "ft",
              "content": [
                "Hebrew nor enlarge your mouth"
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "in the day of their distress."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "13"
        },
        "You should not enter the gate of My people"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "in the day of their disaster,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "nor gloat over their affliction"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "in the day of their disaster,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "nor loot their wealth"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "in the day of their disaster."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "14"
        },
        "Nor should you stand at the crossroads"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "to cut off their fugitives,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "nor deliver up their survivors"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "in the day of their distress."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "s1",
      "content": [
        "The Deliverance of Israel"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "15"
        },
        "For the Day of the LORD is near"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "for all the nations."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "As you have done, it will be done to you;"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "your recompense will return upon your own head."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "16"
        },
        "For as you drank on My holy mountain,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "so all the nations will drink continually."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "They will drink and gulp it down;"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "they will be as if they had never existed."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "17"
        },
        "But on Mount Zion there will be deliverance,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "and it will be holy,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "and the house of Jacob"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "will reclaim their possession."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "18"
        },
        "Then the house of Jacob will be a blazing fire,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "and the house of Joseph a burning flame;"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "but the house of Esau will be stubble—"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "Jacob will set it ablaze and consume it."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "Therefore no survivor will remain"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "from the house of Esau.”"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "qr",
      "content": [
        "For the LORD has spoken."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "19"
        },
        "Those from the Negev will possess the mountains of Esau;"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "those from the foothills",
        {
          "type": "note",
          "marker": "f",
          "caller": "+",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "fr",
              "content": [
                "1:19 "
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "ft",
              "content": [
                "Hebrew Shephelah or lowlands; that is, the western foothills of Judea"
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        " will possess the land of the Philistines."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "They will occupy the fields of Ephraim and Samaria,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "and Benjamin will possess Gilead."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "20"
        },
        "And the exiles of this host of the Israelites"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "will possess the land of the Canaanites as far as Zarephath;"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "and the exiles from Jerusalem who are in Sepharad"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "will possess the cities of the Negev."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "21"
        },
        "The deliverers will ascend",
        {
          "type": "note",
          "marker": "f",
          "caller": "+",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "fr",
              "content": [
                "1:21 "
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "ft",
              "content": [
                "Or The deliverers will go up from; LXX Those being delivered will go up"
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        " Mount Zion"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q2",
      "content": [
        "to rule over the mountains of Esau."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "b"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "q1",
      "content": [
        "And the kingdom will belong to the LORD."
      ]
    }
  ]
}